---
import UberEats from "../../public/Icons/UberEats.astro"
import PedidosYa from "../../public/Icons/PedidosYa.astro"
---

<section class="text-gray-600 body-font h-full">
  <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:pr-10 mb-6 md:mb-0 w-full md:w-auto text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="p-3 font-light text-gray-900 text-xl lg:text-3xl md:text-4xl">Con Hambre?</h2>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-medium title-font text-gray-900 md:text-7xl">Ordena Ahora</h1>
      <p class="justify-center mx-auto my-6 max-w-lg md:max-w-none">Nos hemos asociado con expertos en entregas confiables que manejarán tus pedidos sin problemas.</p>
      <p class="justify-center max-w-lg md:max-w-none">Simplemente visita a tu socio de entrega preferido a través de los enlaces a continuación.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:ml-auto mx-auto items-center flex-shrink-0 space-y-4">
      <a href="https://www.ubereats.com/es/store/biggies-tacos-quito/KUQ86kWlRGOBmcY2J13OVA?diningMode=DELIVERY&sc=SEARCH_SUGGESTION" class="w-full" target="_blank" >
        <button class="bg-green-600 inline-flex py-3 px-5 rounded-lg items-center  focus:outline-none w-full">
          <UberEats />
          <span class="ml-5 flex items-start flex-col leading-none">
            <span class="title-font text-white font-medium">Uber Eats</span>
          </span>
        </button>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.pedidosya.com.ec/restaurantes/quito/biggies-tacos-e0ad751a-b73b-436d-ad91-aa9955777ff5-menu?search=biggies%20tacos" class="w-full" target="_blank">
        <button class="bg-red-500 inline-flex py-3 px-5 rounded-lg items-center  focus:outline-none w-full">
          <PedidosYa />
          <span class="ml-5 flex items-start flex-col leading-none">
            <span class="title-font text-white font-medium">Pedidos Ya</span>
          </span>
        </button>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
